### List All Tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/activities/todolist/tasks

### Create Task
POST http://localhost:3000/activities/todolist/tasks 
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=Complete the project report

### Read Task
GET http://localhost:3000/activities/todolist/tasks/<taskId>

### Update Task
PUT http://localhost:3000/activities/todolist/tasks/<taskId>
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

status=ongoing

### Delete Task
DELETE http://localhost:3000/activities/todolist/tasks/<taskId>

### URL Error Handler
GET http://localhost:3000/activities/todolist/